metadata.name: AOA 1
metadata.description:
The 1st:

ADOR opens, your mind is the key. 

Now is the time for our global community to operate with a common goal... 

Masterful alignment, Magnificent abundance for all that choose this path. 

We are more powerful together, we are the change now. 

We are the source. 

Stand up and witness a new paradigm unfold. For our ancestors have prepared us to empower the next generation, now. 

You are infinite, you are powerful, you are enough. 

Create the life you desire now!

ENJOY.
